<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="use-vt">use <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /juːz/    美 /juːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使用；利用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Time, used correctly, is money in the bank. 
时间，如果使用合理的话，就像银行中的存款。</p><footer>2012 湖南</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>use sth for / as:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Poets use language as a way of expressing their feelings.
诗人用语言作为表达情感的一种方式。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They were using animals for scientific experiments.
他们正在使用动物做科学实验。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>use sth to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A code uses symbols to replace words, phrases, or sentences.
密码使用符号来替代单词、短语或句子。</p><footer>2016 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>发挥；运用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>use all one’s effort 
作出一切努力</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>use one’s brain 
动脑筋</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>耗费；消费：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This type of heater uses a lot of electricity.
这种热水器很费电。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="use-up">use up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>用光；耗尽：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The human race is using up Earth’s resources. 
人类正在耗尽地球上的资源。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t let yesterday use up too much of today. 
今日事，今日毕。</p></div></div>